  "informal_statement": "If two angles are supplementary (sum to π) then each equals π minus the other.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Rearrange the linear equation a + b = π; `linarith`. Bridging the angle relation to scalar arithmetic avoids the nlinarith-on-angle-atoms hazard.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem supplementary_angle (a b : ℝ) (h : a + b = Real.pi) : a = Real.pi - b",
